*Ispod* stola je pao ključ (The key fell under the table).

*Ispod* su se nalazile knjige (There were books underneath).

Učenici su se smestili *ispod* nastavnika (The students settled under the teacher).

Ona je stajala *ispod* lustera (She was standing beneath the chandelier).

Konfuzija je bila *ispod* očekivanog (The confusion was below what was expected).

Užasno je to što se događa *ispod* površine (It's horrifying what's happening beneath the surface).